============================================================
WEIGHTED SUM W(n) = Σ c(n,k) 2^k
============================================================
  n=3: W = 8, W/n! = 4/3, CV² = 1/3 = 0.3333333333
  n=4: W = 32, W/n! = 4/3, CV² = 1/3 = 0.3333333333
  n=5: W = 158, W/n! = 79/60, CV² = 19/60 = 0.3166666667
  n=6: W = 928, W/n! = 58/45, CV² = 13/45 = 0.2888888889
  n=7: W = 6350, W/n! = 635/504, CV² = 131/504 = 0.2599206349

KEY INSIGHT: CV² = W(n)/n! - 1 where W(n) = Σ c(n,k) 2^k
And E[H²]/E[H]² = W(n)/n!

  W(3) = 8
  W(4) = 32
  W(5) = 158
  W(6) = 928
  W(7) = 6350

  W(3)/n! = 4/3
  W(4)/n! = 4/3
  W(5)/n! = 79/60
  W(6)/n! = 58/45
  W(7)/n! = 635/504

W sequence: [8, 32, 158, 928, 6350]

W(n) - n*W(n-1):
  n=4: W(4) - 4*W(3) = 32 - 32 = 0
  n=5: W(5) - 5*W(4) = 158 - 160 = -2
  n=6: W(6) - 6*W(5) = 928 - 948 = -20
  n=7: W(7) - 7*W(6) = 6350 - 6496 = -146

W(n) - n*W(n-1) - (n-1)*W(n-2):
  n=5: -34
  n=6: -180
  n=7: -1094

============================================================
INTERPRETATION: W(n) = Σ_{σ compat with id} 2^{common(id,σ)}
============================================================
W(n)/n! = E[H²]/E[H]² = 1 + CV²

  W(3)/n! = 4/3 = 1.3333333333
  W(4)/n! = 4/3 = 1.3333333333
  W(5)/n! = 79/60 = 1.3166666667
  W(6)/n! = 58/45 = 1.2888888889
  W(7)/n! = 635/504 = 1.2599206349

=== RECHECK W VALUES ===
  n=3: dist=[0, 2, 1], W = Σ c(n,k)×2^k = 0×1 + 2×2 + 1×4 = 8
  n=4: dist=[2, 5, 3, 1], W = Σ c(n,k)×2^k = 2×1 + 5×2 + 3×4 + 1×8 = 32
  n=5: dist=[14, 20, 14, 4, 1], W = Σ c(n,k)×2^k = 14×1 + 20×2 + 14×4 + 4×8 + 1×16 = 158
  n=6: dist=[90, 115, 72, 26, 5, 1], W = Σ c(n,k)×2^k = 90×1 + 115×2 + 72×4 + 26×8 + 5×16 + 1×32 = 928
  n=7: dist=[646, 790, 467, 168, 41, 6, 1], W = Σ c(n,k)×2^k = 646×1 + 790×2 + 467×4 + 168×8 + 41×16 + 6×32 + 1×64 = 6350

